data.expected_result: Either there's an empty space like the server icon in the invite modal or there's Discord's logo like in friends list.
data.short_description: The user management list in server settings is the only list that just has a plain blurple profile picture placeholder.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to a big server where you have manage members permission. - Click on Server settings>Members. - Scroll down through the list with inertia. - Observe the profile pictures of people. -
